column1: ##Project Description=10x Genomics NextGEM Single Cell Multiome ATAC + Gene Expression Human bone, cartilage and synovium nuclei  Sample Date = 6/30/2023 3 Samples (2 ATAC libraries & 3 GEX libraries) 10x Protocol CG000338 Rev F  ATAC libraries: 1. cartilage, target 8,600 nuclei, N index=B1 2. synovium, target 15,700 nuclei, N index=C1 Target 16,400 reads/nuclei = 400 mil reads  NextSeq Flowcell Run 0311 = P2-100 cycle (400 mil) & Target 15,000 reads/nuclei = 400 mil reads NextSeq Flowcell Run 0335 = P2-100 cycle (400 mil)  GEX libraries: 1. bone, target 14,800 nuclei, TT index=F8 2. cartilage, target 8,600 nuclei, TT index=G8 3. synovium, target 15,700 nuclei, TT index=H8 Target 10,200 reads/nuclei = 400 mil reads  NextSeq Flowcell Run 0312 = P2-100 cycle (400 mil)
##Analysis Notes=Would you prefer to receive a bcl files and/or a fastq files?	fastq file
